title: Windows 7-8-8.1 + Office 2010-2013 loader/serials/activations
description:
Every tool I have been able to use to activate Windows 7, 8, 8.1, Office 2010 and 2013.

For Windows 7: 
-Open Windows 7 Loader
-Open Windows Loader.exe
-Click on install and restart PC on prompt.

For Windows 8:
-Serials for installation provided (Windows 8 Pro 64b)
-Open Office 2013 - Windows 8 hack.exe
-Press Windows button
-Try either on Activation or Product Keys to activate. Activation is for VL versions so it will have to be redone in 6 months.

For Windows 8.1:
-Open Windows 8.1 KMS-serial
-Serials for installation provided (Windows 8.1 Pro 64b - "W8.1 installation serial.txt")
-Serials for KMS attempts provided ("Win81-pkeys.txt")
-Try either Professional Server 1, 2 or 3, one will almost always work. Activation is for VL versions so it will have to be redone in 6 months.

For Office 2010/2013:
-Open Office 2013 - Windows 8 hack.exe
-Press Office button
-Try either on Activation or Product Keys (here you can choose either Office 2010 or 2013)

Hope you can use this, I'm able to activate every program mentioned above. None of this was made by me, it's what I've found  with intense searches lots  of times.

Please share as I'm doing and SEED so others can use this too!
